quran[3]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,43,"Ẹ kírun, ẹ yọ zakāh, kí ẹ sì dáwọ́tẹ orúnkún pẹ̀lú àwọn olùdáwọ́tẹ-orúnkún (lórí ìrun).",footnotes:1:¹ Ẹ̀rí ìrun jama'ah
  2,44,"Ṣé ẹ̀yin yóò máa pa àwọn ènìyàn l’áṣẹ ohun rere, ẹ sì ń gbàgbé ẹ̀mí ara yín, ẹ̀yin sì ń ké Tírà, ṣé ẹ kò ṣe làákàyè ni!"
  2,45,"Ẹ wá oore (Allāhu) pẹ̀lú sùúrùàti ìrun kíkí. Dájúdájú ó lágbára (láti ṣe bẹ́ẹ̀) àyàfi fún àwọn olùpáyà (Allāhu), {1}",footnotes:1:Mẹ́ta ni sùúrù yìí pín sí. Ìkíní: Dídúró ṣinṣin nínú ẹ̀sìn ’Islām. Ìkejì: Ṣíṣe ìfaradà lórí àdánwò àti níní àtẹ̀mọ́ra ìnira. Ìkẹta: Sísá fún ẹ̀ṣẹ̀.